data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="450">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$you-tao-79-28" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/you-tao-79-28" class="zg-link" title="油桃">油桃</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-ming-bin" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-ming-bin" class="zg-link" title="陈铭彬">陈铭彬</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$duo-xi-wang" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/duo-xi-wang" class="zg-link" title="多希望">多希望</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2408083" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">首先是行为举止，要落落大方不怯场，公共场合敢于把头抬起来。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/cbcab33fce807a57f5516a515d489368_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/cbcab33fce807a57f5516a515d489368_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/cbcab33fce807a57f5516a515d489368_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/cbcab33fce807a57f5516a515d489368_b.jpg"><br>更重要的是内涵，要多学才艺，陶冶情操。比如会唱歌。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/b4d336211a567233fa319b7b3e02d965_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/b4d336211a567233fa319b7b3e02d965_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/b4d336211a567233fa319b7b3e02d965_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/b4d336211a567233fa319b7b3e02d965_b.jpg"><br>会下一盘很大的棋。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/2a824b26634535386efcb076e8491832_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/2a824b26634535386efcb076e8491832_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/2a824b26634535386efcb076e8491832_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/2a824b26634535386efcb076e8491832_b.jpg"><br>最重要的还是必须有文化。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/3bcdc8900fa21c6d1b08abe728bf55c2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/3bcdc8900fa21c6d1b08abe728bf55c2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/3bcdc8900fa21c6d1b08abe728bf55c2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/3bcdc8900fa21c6d1b08abe728bf55c2_b.jpg"><br>同时要始终保持一颗谦卑的心。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/2ec140c4ef48532a99becdef26187681_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="220" data-rawheight="350" class="content_image" width="220"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="220" data-rawheight="350" class="content_image lazy" width="220" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/2ec140c4ef48532a99becdef26187681_b.jpg"><br><br>培养女儿这个问题啊，小看不得。曾仕强教授很早就给我们总结过了。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/be0f7df8e5b21d2cc389cb5a84d0de34_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/be0f7df8e5b21d2cc389cb5a84d0de34_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8059de4e8ccbbc30014a35d673aba90_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/a8059de4e8ccbbc30014a35d673aba90_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/7b8c5f2f23bce0fdc10c21e1959278fc_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="298" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/7b8c5f2f23bce0fdc10c21e1959278fc_b.jpg"><br>天亮了。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/8e6b45c352ca5fe9f84566dfb93fbfd3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/8e6b45c352ca5fe9f84566dfb93fbfd3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/8e6b45c352ca5fe9f84566dfb93fbfd3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/8e6b45c352ca5fe9f84566dfb93fbfd3_b.jpg">


